    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really solid shape! It drives like a dream and has been super well-loved over the years. If you're looking for a dependable car that's ready for its next adventure without breaking the bank, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat and show it to you!",
