    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted example of the legendary S54 platform. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features individual throttle bodies and a Double-VANOS system, providing exceptional throttle response up to an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and an M Variable Differential Lock. This chassis has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and a cooling system refresh. The suspension geometry remains taut with upgraded bushings, ensuring precise turn-in and high-speed stability. An ideal choice for the enthusiast seeking a high-performance driver with its major mechanical milestones addressed.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
