    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my car, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a reliable companion. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape and drives like a dream\u2014perfect for anyone who wants a solid, dependable ride that still looks great in the driveway! I\u2019ve taken care of it over the years, and it's ready to hit the road for plenty more adventures with you. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
