    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant. This high-revving 3.2L inline-six remains visceral, benefiting from a recent VANOS system overhaul and rod bearing replacement for preventative longevity. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential that ensures optimal torque distribution. Suspension geometry remains tight with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, while the subframe has been proactively reinforced\u2014a critical upgrade for this chassis. While showing light patina consistent with a well-enjoyed driver\u2019s car, the mechanical integrity and linear throttle response across the 8,000 RPM range are exceptional. A purist-spec example ready for the twisties.",
